<section id="fb2">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>rose</b>: The past simple tense is needed.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb3">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>downward</b>: Older age groups use the Internet less.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb4">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>steadily</b>: The adverb is needed.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb5">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>plunged</b>: The figures fell dramatically.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb6">
